{"tid":2069400,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)星際傳奇1-3","createTime":"2020-06-18T10:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T20:07:12.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fee5321be898405bffe88619c4a4b0f4c56af9bc","tid":2069400,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=50e3a28b\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c6dcef12\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=abe7f48f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/tsuyuan123/28d802aabba5d96173d30fc41cd52052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ftsuyuan123%2F28d802aabba5d96173d30fc41cd52052.jpg&h=6ae6b100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.太空船獵人號，在航行中遭隕石擊中不得不迫降在鄰近的行星上，四十名旅客中只有十二人存活，其中包括女船員卡洛琳&middot;佛雷、一名穆斯林長老，以及殺人犯里察&middot;雷迪，和押解他的警員強斯。 當他們在有三個太陽的星球上尋找水源，雷迪逃脫。眾人在搜尋時，其中一名留守乘客齊克，誤殺一名之前迫降星球時飛出船艙的倖存者，在埋葬被誤殺的倖存者時遭到不明生物虐殺。眾人本以為是雷迪下手，但最後發現在這星球地底下有一群畏懼光線，但十分凶惡的異形....<br />\n<br />\n2.電影劇情緊接上一集，殺人疑犯Riddick在事發五年之後仍未逃離那個充滿危險的星際，而且還被僱傭的賞金獵人追捕，因為他現在的項上人頭已值150萬，而出這筆賞金的卻是一個他曾經救過的人。後Riddick奪得賞金獵人們的飛船，前往首陽星查明原因。當來到首陽星時，又從一個元素使者那裡得知，原來是她預測到了馬歇爾王即將攻擊首陽星，所以才以此方式將Riddick吸引到首陽星上。可是Riddick到來還沒多久，馬歇爾王的大軍就已開到，並開始大肆攻擊首陽星，而Riddick也開始了拯救宇宙之戰....<br />\n<br />\n3.惡名昭彰的雷迪克（馮迪索飾）被同伴背叛後，獨自被放逐到銀河系上一個只有焦黑土壤的死亡星球，但很快的，前所未見的驚人變種怪物找上了他，在面臨這群比起之前所有敵人都還可怕的嗜血怪物的情況下，為了生存，他迫不得已只能選擇啟動一個裝置，而這也將引來所有為了得到重賞而一直追殺他的星際傭兵。爾後，雷迪克就開始了一場又一場的勢死之戰，與賞金獵人展開對決。<br />\n<br />\n7 10PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=b532ef87\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=030b953a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea74a8579ca4b7a7c49202312e49da74da3a0ad","tid":2069400,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"